{"TopicId":5237,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"Recreate the Arkbird","CreatedByName":"cardgame","CreatedById":12317,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-07T21:05:07Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"cardgame","CreatedById":12317,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-07T21:05:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E...should know what I\\\u0027m talking about.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe Arkbird is an orbital plane that descends into the upper atmosphere to change course. It is armed with a laser cannon on its belly or nose. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIn the original game, it was put into space via mass drivers. Here, the challenge is to put it into space with a rocket or two, or even by itself. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.freewebs.com/gahrodanth/ArkbirdKC144.png\u0022 alt=\u0022ArkbirdKC144.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110805074928/acecombat/images/a/ab/Arkbird.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022Arkbird.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBuild the spaceplane as close to scale as you can. It is completely understandable if you are unable to construct a 200 meter monster, but larger is better.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"crekit","CreatedById":5097,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-07T21:20:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ETo scale after adjusting for a kerbels smaller size? That would seem fair.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Luigibro606","CreatedById":8700,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-07T21:32:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOh, I remember that. Never could beat the level.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NeoHoltsky","CreatedById":11782,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-07T21:49:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThat takes me back. Hated that giant laser in the back. All of NESA\\\u0027s resources shall be devoted to creating this monster!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Golakka","CreatedById":12833,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-08T01:00:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThis is the best ive managed so far\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAttempting to gain orbit\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/ci3Pc.png\u0022 alt=\u0022ci3Pc.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHead on shot\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/N7Ktd.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022N7Ktd.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDropping low into the atmosphere\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/pjzDF.png\u0022 alt=\u0022pjzDF.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBurning back out again\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/ZFISf.png\u0022 alt=\u0022ZFISf.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESustained damage from unknown source\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/s9PSC.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022s9PSC.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EScrew you Blaze\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Xr3SI.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022Xr3SI.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cardgame","CreatedById":12317,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-08T02:11:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EPretty nice design. I\\\u0027m surprised you were able to control it so well without a tailfin \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBy outer atmosphere, though, I mean up at 50,000\u002B meters, or as high as it is possible to be and still change your plane\\\u0027s heading without RCS. By orbital plane, I mean it should be able to establish itself in an orbit exceeding 75,000 meters.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Golakka","CreatedById":12833,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-08T03:00:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYeah, im a few more days tinkering away from a stable orbit \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EActually the inclined surface aera provides enough stability\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-08T03:26:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIs the engine located underneath or in the wings?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cardgame","CreatedById":12317,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-08T03:31:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThose yellow dots are the engine locations. There are some right where the angled wings separate from the larger main wing, above and below the wing.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-08T05:45:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EClosest I can get.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i548.photobucket.com/albums/ii353/eL_pAmBaTo25/KSP2012-01-0813-28-34-64.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022KSP2012-01-0813-28-34-64.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i548.photobucket.com/albums/ii353/eL_pAmBaTo25/KSP2012-01-0813-28-47-40.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022KSP2012-01-0813-28-47-40.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i548.photobucket.com/albums/ii353/eL_pAmBaTo25/KSP2012-01-0813-29-39-97.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022KSP2012-01-0813-29-39-97.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i548.photobucket.com/albums/ii353/eL_pAmBaTo25/KSP2012-01-0813-29-44-99.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022KSP2012-01-0813-29-44-99.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i548.photobucket.com/albums/ii353/eL_pAmBaTo25/KSP2012-01-0813-34-41-38.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022KSP2012-01-0813-34-41-38.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI think I\\\u0027ve paid too much attention in the wings and underbelly...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI like to put that thing in orbit\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022459\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/WeFyAe-0AQQ?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E, but I just can\\\u0027t because of the tanks below.\u003Cp\u003EAnd \u003Cem\u003Eit flies like a goddamn brick.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cardgame","CreatedById":12317,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-08T06:36:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIt\\\u0027s supposed to fly like a brick \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt\\\u0027s an orbital plane, not a fighter jet.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Golakka","CreatedById":12833,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-08T06:43:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThe construction isnt the problem, tis getting an incredibly un-airworthy machine into orbit.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-08T15:34:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ERevamped the previous one. Removed the belly engines and put 2 tanks in its wings. Now it can be \u0027shuttled\u0027.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i548.photobucket.com/albums/ii353/eL_pAmBaTo25/KSP2012-01-0822-57-10-70.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022KSP2012-01-0822-57-10-70.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\\\u0027ve managed to trick the collision mesh by removing the rest of the wing while putting the side tanks and putting it in a way that it won\\\u0027t touch neither sides. All\\\u0027s perfect now.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i548.photobucket.com/albums/ii353/eL_pAmBaTo25/KSP2012-01-0823-00-35-00.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022KSP2012-01-0823-00-35-00.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i548.photobucket.com/albums/ii353/eL_pAmBaTo25/KSP2012-01-0823-00-41-50.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022KSP2012-01-0823-00-41-50.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i548.photobucket.com/albums/ii353/eL_pAmBaTo25/KSP2012-01-0823-01-21-06.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022KSP2012-01-0823-01-21-06.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i548.photobucket.com/albums/ii353/eL_pAmBaTo25/KSP2012-01-0823-01-00-86.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022KSP2012-01-0823-01-00-86.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIf you\\\u0027re wondering what\\\u0027s up with the clusterf*** of struts, this is what the plane looks like in flight if I will not put that much.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i548.photobucket.com/albums/ii353/eL_pAmBaTo25/KSP2012-01-0822-34-36-09.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022KSP2012-01-0822-34-36-09.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESo yea, probably the closest I\\\u0027ve did \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tim_Barrett","CreatedById":3206,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-08T17:02:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhen you remove the struts, the wings flap violently and randomly; a kerbal bird!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-08T17:30:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tim_Barrett\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Tim_Barrett\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhen you remove the struts, the wings flap violently and randomly; a kerbal bird!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETouche \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt does still shake, although minimal. But \u003Cem\u003Eit\\\u0027ll rattle the entire plane\u003C/em\u003E when it does. \u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Joshmo","CreatedById":10280,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-09T01:11:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EGood challenge!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cardgame","CreatedById":12317,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-10T18:51:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThanks \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECare to submit an entry?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-12T10:59:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESo who has the closest yet? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Joshmo","CreatedById":10280,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-12T16:29:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI haven\\\u0027t quite gotten anything to fly very well yet.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cardgame","CreatedById":12317,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-12T17:04:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Flixxbeatz\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Flixxbeatz\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESo who has the closest yet? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EProbably your second entry.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Joshmo","CreatedById":10280,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-12T17:38:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Golakka\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Golakka\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis is the best ive managed so far\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAttempting to gain orbit\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/ci3Pc.png\u0022 alt=\u0022ci3Pc.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHead on shot\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/N7Ktd.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022N7Ktd.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDropping low into the atmosphere\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/pjzDF.png\u0022 alt=\u0022pjzDF.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBurning back out again\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/ZFISf.png\u0022 alt=\u0022ZFISf.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESustained damage from unknown source\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/s9PSC.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022s9PSC.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EScrew you Blaze\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Xr3SI.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022Xr3SI.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis one gets my vote\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cardgame","CreatedById":12317,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-01-12T18:25:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIt\\\u0027s a tough decision. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ehint to any more contenders: the Arkbird\\\u0027s flaps are very long and narrow... kind of like a certain flap ingame with 0.9 lift \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Swizzlewizzle","CreatedById":68507,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-30T11:59:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI got pretty close. Would have loved to get rid of all the stupid massive fuel tanks but there is no way to create molded fuel tanks yet... the wings were created with the \u0022Procedural Wings\u0022 plugin allowing for custom wing shapes. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI made it as big as possible.... heavy planes like this take a LOT of jet engines to get off the ground \u0026gt;.\u0026lt;\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/y1rnuc2.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022y1rnuc2.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/0qDgxKR.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00220qDgxKR.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/U1q0K5J.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022U1q0K5J.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OtherDalfite","CreatedById":8317,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-30T22:11:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOh wow, haven\u0027t seen this thread in a long time. I guess if people are still contributing to it, I see no need for it to be locked.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Swizzlewizzle","CreatedById":68507,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T00:38:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OtherDalfite\u0022 data-cite=\u0022OtherDalfite\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EOh wow, haven\u0027t seen this thread in a long time. I guess if people are still contributing to it, I see no need for it to be locked.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe arkbird is a really nice space plane. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}